message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper deals with deep learning based image segmentation methods and their application in clinical practice, which suggests that it is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of MR imaging in the context of cardiovascular disease suggests that it may also belong to the medical imaging (cs.MED) sub-category. Finally, the use of neural networks for prediction suggests that it may also belong to the neural networks (cs.NEURON) sub-category.
